Name, last name, email, address, country, IP address, subscription information, join date, conversation history, support tickets.
Services to Send Transactional Emails
First name, last name, email, transactional event details (e.g., password reset, invoice sent).
Services to Send Marketing Emails and Newsletters
First name, last name, email, subset of platform events, subscription information, marketing preferences.
Search Functionality
IP address, browser information, search queries, click data, timestamps.
Performance Monitoring
IP address, browser information, session metrics, device information, page load times.
Analytics Services
IP address, browser information, anonymized identifiers, session data, page visits, time spent on platform.
